snippet.title: Johnny Depp And Amber Heard's Settlement
snippet.description:
After Amber Heard filed for divorce from Johnny Depp back in May 2016, the former Hollywood couple have finally agreed on a settlement - just in time for Depp to launch an entire new lawsuit.
